WEBVTT

00:07.760 --> 00:08.960
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.360 --> 01:42.520
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVE
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:46.040 --> 01:49.480
ONE MONTH EARLIER

02:03.920 --> 02:04.840
Stay still.

02:06.000 --> 02:07.520
The wound is just starting to scab.

02:12.120 --> 02:13.240
Take it easy.

02:17.560 --> 02:18.640
I am alive?

02:18.720 --> 02:20.600
Yes. Even the Underworld

02:20.680 --> 02:22.480
wouldn't dare claim a soul
with such a baleful aura.

02:23.520 --> 02:27.120
It’s good you’re still alive.
Being alive is a blessing.

02:27.640 --> 02:30.040
Here, have some water.

02:37.720 --> 02:39.040
Careful.

02:40.120 --> 02:44.280
The wound missed your heart by a hair.

02:47.440 --> 02:48.640
What about the Northern Desert King?

02:48.720 --> 02:49.960
Nothing left to bury.

02:50.040 --> 02:51.880
With the internal strife over there,

02:51.960 --> 02:53.280
they will not be able
to bother us for a while.

02:58.960 --> 03:01.120
Do not move. Why are you so stubborn?

03:01.200 --> 03:02.040
Lie back down.

03:02.560 --> 03:03.520
I must go back.

03:04.040 --> 03:06.800
I know you are longing to see Zhao.

03:06.880 --> 03:09.720
But surviving comes first, alright?

03:10.240 --> 03:12.920
The Capital is in turmoil,
but rest assured.

03:13.440 --> 03:15.760
I will find someone
to let her know you are alive.

03:15.840 --> 03:17.760
Besides, if you go there now,

03:17.840 --> 03:19.560
how would you protect her?

03:24.240 --> 03:25.400
<i>Zhao,</i>

03:26.680 --> 03:27.640
<i>wait for me.</i>

03:33.440 --> 03:35.840
ONE DAY EARLIER

03:37.600 --> 03:38.560
<i>Jiu.</i>

03:40.720 --> 03:42.120
<i>The moon is full again.</i>

04:27.600 --> 04:28.440
Jiu.

04:53.160 --> 04:54.480
It really is you.

05:02.360 --> 05:03.200
It's me.

05:28.440 --> 05:29.880
Your Highness, you shouldn't go.

05:34.840 --> 05:36.880
Xie Yanfang has been plotting for so long,

05:38.120 --> 05:40.360
all for this trap at the hunting grounds.

05:41.840 --> 05:43.200
If I don't walk into it,

05:44.040 --> 05:45.320
how can he reveal his true colors?

05:46.040 --> 05:47.720
What if he truly intends to kill you?

05:55.880 --> 05:56.960
Then I'll bet

06:00.280 --> 06:01.360
on who can outlast

06:03.040 --> 06:04.360
the other.

06:09.600 --> 06:10.880
Yanlai?

06:13.040 --> 06:14.480
You're alive.

06:17.360 --> 06:19.920
Xie Yanfang.

06:21.240 --> 06:22.640
Frontier Troops, heed my command.

06:24.800 --> 06:25.560
FRONTIER TROOPS TOKEN

06:25.640 --> 06:26.360
This is

06:27.480 --> 06:29.280
the Token to mobilize the frontier troops.

06:29.360 --> 06:32.560
Seize the rebel, Xie Yanlai, at once.

06:49.640 --> 06:51.520
You have survived a brush with death.

06:52.960 --> 06:54.840
How gratifying.

06:56.640 --> 06:57.480
It's a pity, though,

06:59.640 --> 07:01.520
that someone will die.

07:04.240 --> 07:05.040
Do not harm her!

07:06.600 --> 07:07.440
What,

07:10.080 --> 07:12.080
does your heart ache for her?

07:13.280 --> 07:14.960
Then go die in her stead,

07:15.040 --> 07:18.600
using this poisoned dagger
Her Highness prepared for the two of us.

07:18.680 --> 07:19.880
Don't listen to him.

07:20.400 --> 07:21.880
Frontier Troops, heed my command.

07:21.960 --> 07:23.520
-Execute…
-Your Highness, have you forgotten

07:24.720 --> 07:26.880
the Frontier Troops
answer only to this token?

07:26.960 --> 07:29.280
You told me that yourself.

07:34.120 --> 07:35.280
Yanlai.

07:36.360 --> 07:38.440
-Do it!
-Stop!

07:41.920 --> 07:42.840
Don't.

07:52.800 --> 07:55.200
Don't. The dagger is poisoned.

07:55.880 --> 07:59.280
Indeed, the Golden Finch Venom
has no cure.

08:00.480 --> 08:02.600
Think carefully

08:03.640 --> 08:06.640
whether her life is worth yours.

08:07.160 --> 08:09.920
No. Jiu, don't.

08:10.520 --> 08:12.360
-Jiu.
-Will you keep

08:14.400 --> 08:15.640
your word?

08:16.680 --> 08:18.080
-Certainly.
-Jiu.

08:18.920 --> 08:20.200
Don't.

08:20.960 --> 08:23.680
The dagger is poisoned. Don't.

08:38.200 --> 08:39.039
That will do.

08:48.400 --> 08:49.320
Let them leave.

08:57.920 --> 09:00.240
Mr. Xie, why let them go?

09:00.320 --> 09:02.240
I want to see

09:04.280 --> 09:08.960
how a cornered beast
breaks out of its cage.

09:11.600 --> 09:14.520
Mr. Xie, please take this first.

09:29.920 --> 09:31.040
Jiu.

09:31.120 --> 09:34.000
Jiu. Jiu. Jiu.

09:34.800 --> 09:36.520
Jiu. Jiu.

09:36.600 --> 09:38.040
Jiu.

09:45.040 --> 09:46.080
I'm sorry.

09:47.040 --> 09:48.600
I feel utterly useless

09:49.840 --> 09:52.120
for failing to kill Xie Yanfang for you.

09:53.440 --> 09:54.880
Don't worry about me.

09:57.320 --> 09:58.360
Go.

09:59.560 --> 10:01.520
-Go.
-Jiu, don't fall asleep.

10:01.600 --> 10:03.440
I don't need you to kill him for me. Jiu.

10:04.440 --> 10:06.160
We were of the same blood.

10:07.160 --> 10:09.360
Yanlai, I must trouble you

10:10.760 --> 10:12.800
to join me on the road to the afterlife.

10:14.360 --> 10:15.640
Chu Zhao,

10:16.240 --> 10:20.160
can we have a proper talk now?

10:21.000 --> 10:25.800
Do you truly wish
to watch him die in such agony?

10:26.960 --> 10:29.400
I know the Golden Finch Venom.

10:30.000 --> 10:31.520
As it takes effect,

10:31.600 --> 10:34.040
it feels like fire
burning through one's internal organs

10:35.000 --> 10:37.280
before one coughs up blood and dies.

10:37.360 --> 10:39.640
His face will contort,

10:40.760 --> 10:42.360
his body will wither,

10:42.960 --> 10:46.680
and he will die slowly in agony.

10:46.760 --> 10:48.840
-Chu Zhao.
-Zhao, don't listen to him.

10:50.080 --> 10:51.720
Do you want to save him?

10:51.800 --> 10:53.160
Zhao.

10:55.400 --> 10:56.880
Don't listen to him.

10:57.480 --> 11:00.040
He came for you, and he is dying for you.

11:00.120 --> 11:02.640
Do you really not want to save him?

11:04.600 --> 11:06.440
You should.

11:10.800 --> 11:13.200
This is
the Nanjiang Millennium Snow Lingzhi.

11:14.000 --> 11:15.320
It can keep him alive.

11:15.920 --> 11:17.240
As long as I live,

11:19.560 --> 11:21.280
so shall he.

11:24.320 --> 11:25.400
Zhao.

11:25.480 --> 11:27.640
How ironic.

11:27.720 --> 11:29.680
You intended to kill me,

11:30.760 --> 11:33.640
yet you've ended up
killing your most beloved.

11:35.000 --> 11:35.960
Zhao.

11:37.160 --> 11:38.120
Zhao.

11:39.960 --> 11:41.720
Don't listen to him.

11:41.800 --> 11:43.360
I'm not afraid of death.

11:44.680 --> 11:47.560
Don't agree to his terms. I beg you.

12:07.520 --> 12:08.560
Zhao.

12:14.680 --> 12:16.000
Are you still

12:17.640 --> 12:19.480
thinking of killing me?

12:22.160 --> 12:23.480
Then think carefully.

12:25.640 --> 12:26.760
If I die,

12:27.800 --> 12:29.520
Yanlai dies with me.

12:30.280 --> 12:31.560
Will you kill me,

12:32.160 --> 12:34.160
or save your beloved?

12:36.800 --> 12:40.320
Just promise to return to court

12:41.560 --> 12:43.560
and serve as a puppet for the Xie Clan,

12:44.960 --> 12:46.960
and I shall sustain his life.

12:48.400 --> 12:50.720
I can hand Yu

12:51.360 --> 12:53.840
and the State of Chu to you.

12:58.520 --> 12:59.560
Zhao.

13:01.280 --> 13:02.880
Do you remember…

13:04.200 --> 13:05.720
your promise…

13:07.240 --> 13:08.560
to grant me a wish?

13:11.160 --> 13:12.200
I want you

13:13.920 --> 13:15.480
to refuse his terms.

13:16.680 --> 13:19.760
From now on, whatever wish you hold,
you may ask it of me.

13:19.840 --> 13:23.760
Come fire or high water,
I will see it fulfilled.

13:25.200 --> 13:28.880
I honor my promises and never renege.

14:00.040 --> 14:01.560
Forgive me, Jiu.

14:02.680 --> 14:03.760
I had

14:04.880 --> 14:06.560
to break my word now.

14:24.960 --> 14:27.320
Jiu. Jiu.

14:51.960 --> 14:54.800
<i>In court, you follow my lead from here on.</i>

14:55.760 --> 14:58.680
<i>Only then can Yanlai's life be guaranteed.</i>

15:03.320 --> 15:05.800
<i>Frontier troop stipends</i>
<i>shall be reduced by 30%,</i>

15:05.880 --> 15:06.720
TAIJI HALL

15:06.800 --> 15:08.520
<i>and the funds shall be redirected</i>
<i>to the southern grain transport.</i>

15:09.320 --> 15:12.040
Frontier troop stipends
shall be reduced by 30%,

15:12.120 --> 15:13.880
and the funds shall be redirected
to the southern grain transport.

15:14.480 --> 15:16.440
<i>Xie Xuan from the Xie Clan…</i>

15:17.320 --> 15:18.600
Xie Xuan from the Xie Clan…

15:19.440 --> 15:21.880
<i>…is promoted to Senior Counselor</i>
<i>of the Grand Commandant's Office…</i>

15:21.960 --> 15:24.000
<i>…is promoted to Senior Counselor</i>
<i>of the Grand Commandant's Office…</i>

15:24.720 --> 15:26.160
<i>…effective immediately.</i>

15:26.880 --> 15:27.720
<i>…effective immediately.</i>

15:27.800 --> 15:28.640
RECOMMEND XIE XUAN TO THE COMMANDANT.
PROPOSE 20% MORE TAX THIS AUTUMN.

15:28.720 --> 15:31.720
<i>This year's autumn tax</i>
<i>shall be raised by 20%</i>

15:31.800 --> 15:33.160
<i>to fill the state treasury.</i>

15:33.680 --> 15:36.000
This year's autumn tax
shall be raised by 20%

15:36.600 --> 15:38.080
to fill the state treasury.

15:38.160 --> 15:41.160
Your Highness, the frontier
is bracing for war.

15:41.240 --> 15:43.800
Cutting military pay at such a time
may not be wise.

15:46.880 --> 15:49.960
<i>The Northern Desert has withdrawn.</i>
<i>The frontier stands secure.</i>

15:50.480 --> 15:52.160
<i>No need for surplus military expenditure.</i>

15:55.000 --> 15:58.000
<i>The Northern Desert has withdrawn.</i>
<i>The frontier stands secure.</i>

15:59.080 --> 16:00.960
No need for surplus military expenditure.

16:03.480 --> 16:06.920
I believe Her Highness has a valid point.

16:07.800 --> 16:09.920
-Seconded.
-Seconded.

16:11.280 --> 16:12.640
Then it is settled.

16:13.520 --> 16:14.920
What does Your Majesty think?

16:16.080 --> 16:17.960
The Grand Princess
has considered everything.

16:18.480 --> 16:19.320
I am reassured.

16:44.080 --> 16:45.920
Your Majesty is still growing.

16:46.440 --> 16:47.320
Do eat more.

16:50.080 --> 16:52.120
-I dreamed of Uncle Yanlai yesterday.
-One does not speak while eating.

16:54.240 --> 16:56.040
-He was teaching me…
-Your Majesty.

16:58.280 --> 17:00.800
If anyone deserves your consideration,
it is Uncle Yanfang.

17:01.400 --> 17:03.040
It is his supervision
of the canal transport

17:03.560 --> 17:05.800
that keeps the grain
from Jiangnan flowing.

17:06.560 --> 17:10.160
Without the Xie Family,
how could this state ever stand firm?

17:10.800 --> 17:12.240
Is Uncle Yanlai still alive?

17:21.800 --> 17:23.400
I will not let him die.

17:26.480 --> 17:28.960
The soup has grown cold. Fetch a hot one.

17:44.240 --> 17:47.560
She's handled all matters you entrusted
during this morning's court session.

17:48.240 --> 17:50.040
She has an excellent memory.

17:51.640 --> 17:52.800
At tomorrow's court,

17:53.560 --> 17:55.480
propose a 30% increase
in commercial taxes,

17:56.360 --> 17:58.080
citing the reasons stated above.

17:59.720 --> 18:01.240
Has the medicine been delivered
to Cangmu Stronghold?

18:01.320 --> 18:03.280
They have collected it.

18:04.640 --> 18:06.440
I gave Chu Zhao my word.

18:06.960 --> 18:08.720
As long as I draw breath,

18:10.160 --> 18:11.600
Yanlai shall not die.

18:15.600 --> 18:18.120
I cannot break faith with her.

18:32.520 --> 18:33.480
Your Highness,

18:34.640 --> 18:36.680
Mr. Xie vomited blood again this morning.

18:37.560 --> 18:41.560
The Imperial Physician fears
he may not survive the winter.

18:43.040 --> 18:45.360
How many days remain

18:46.720 --> 18:47.680
until His Majesty's 12th birthday?

18:48.360 --> 18:49.520
Your Highness.

18:50.040 --> 18:51.720
Twenty-five days.

18:55.760 --> 18:57.360
Twenty-five days.

19:08.520 --> 19:09.680
It seems

19:11.960 --> 19:13.520
I cannot pull through after all.

19:13.600 --> 19:15.960
Mr. Xie, please do not say
such ominous things.

19:18.000 --> 19:20.480
Why fear death?

19:22.960 --> 19:24.960
Yu is about to take the reins himself,

19:26.760 --> 19:28.200
and he carries

19:29.320 --> 19:31.440
the blood of the Xie Family.

19:31.520 --> 19:33.320
Yet should anything happen to you,

19:33.400 --> 19:34.920
and Her Highness seizes this chance
to consolidate power…

19:37.360 --> 19:39.800
I sacrificed so many lives

19:40.320 --> 19:43.480
to forge an emperor from the Xie Family.

19:44.400 --> 19:46.240
I will not let that effort go to waste.

19:47.560 --> 19:50.640
No one can resist the allure of power,

19:51.920 --> 19:56.040
especially a young emperor.

19:56.960 --> 19:59.600
A true emperor

20:00.560 --> 20:03.200
will never endure
being a puppet for a lifetime.

20:04.400 --> 20:06.840
Once Yu assumes direct rule,

20:07.680 --> 20:11.560
he will never tolerate
Chu Zhao's manipulation.

20:13.640 --> 20:18.000
When the time comes,
we shall give him one final push.

20:20.080 --> 20:22.320
I have an agreement with Yu.

20:24.120 --> 20:27.040
The very first decree
he issues upon assuming direct rule

20:29.200 --> 20:32.360
shall be the annihilation of the Chu Clan.

20:38.320 --> 20:39.400
Your Majesty,

20:40.960 --> 20:42.120
the military treatise…

20:43.720 --> 20:45.400
I have no desire
to learn such things today.

20:49.600 --> 20:51.200
Uncle Yanfang said

20:51.880 --> 20:54.480
that reading people
is like reading the stars.

20:58.200 --> 20:59.360
Your Majesty,

21:00.360 --> 21:02.280
the art of reading the stars
is for the imperial astronomers.

21:06.440 --> 21:07.360
Grand Princess,

21:07.960 --> 21:10.600
I am the ruler, and you are my subject.

21:13.640 --> 21:15.720
Your Majesty will soon assume direct rule

21:15.800 --> 21:17.720
and must weigh all matters carefully.

21:17.800 --> 21:18.720
This is for your good.

21:20.280 --> 21:21.320
For my good?

21:21.960 --> 21:23.840
Search your heart.

21:24.360 --> 21:26.200
Do you truly hope for me to rule,

21:26.880 --> 21:30.880
or are you desperate for me
to remain a puppet emperor

21:30.960 --> 21:33.440
so you may keep the reins of power?

21:34.560 --> 21:35.760
Your Majesty,

21:35.840 --> 21:37.360
-I have never…
-Never?

21:37.960 --> 21:41.960
Why do you act with such high-handedness
whenever I face critical affairs of state?

21:42.040 --> 21:45.840
Why do you obstruct me at every turn
whenever I propose a different course?

21:46.960 --> 21:51.320
Chu Zhao, is the taste
of absolute power so sweet

21:51.400 --> 21:55.760
that you never intended to let go?

22:02.520 --> 22:04.200
Is that truly how Your Majesty sees me?

22:04.280 --> 22:05.240
Enough.

22:06.280 --> 22:07.600
Save your excuses.

22:08.520 --> 22:11.440
Guards, escort the Grand Princess
back to her palace

22:12.600 --> 22:14.000
and confine her there to reflect
on her transgressions.

22:22.440 --> 22:23.480
Your Majesty,

22:24.640 --> 22:26.760
please forgive my presumption.

22:38.560 --> 22:40.680
<i>Just as Young Master Yanfang expected.</i>

22:43.120 --> 22:45.560
TAIJI HALL

22:53.800 --> 22:57.000
DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

23:08.520 --> 23:10.120
Kneel.

23:11.440 --> 23:15.080
We congratulate Your Majesty
on assuming direct rule.

23:18.400 --> 23:20.400
Ministers, rise.

23:21.360 --> 23:23.200
-Thank you, Your Majesty.
-Thank you, Your Majesty.

23:23.720 --> 23:27.520
My elder sister entered Taiji Hall bearing
the decree of supervising the court

23:28.240 --> 23:30.160
and governed in my stead.

23:30.240 --> 23:34.120
Now that the land is at peace
and I have assumed my rule,

23:34.200 --> 23:35.920
she has earned her rest.

23:45.480 --> 23:48.200
‎DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

24:00.400 --> 24:03.920
I, Chu Zhao, congratulate Your Majesty
on assuming direct rule.

24:23.800 --> 24:24.840
‎GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

24:25.440 --> 24:27.480
I have an edict to announce.

24:29.400 --> 24:32.360
Why would His Majesty
deliver it in person?

24:33.040 --> 24:35.920
It is the first decree
of His Majesty's direct rule.

24:36.000 --> 24:37.120
It is of great significance.

24:38.520 --> 24:41.680
Upon receiving this divine charge
to govern the state,

24:41.760 --> 24:43.040
I remain ever diligent,

24:43.120 --> 24:45.000
my thoughts centered solely
on the state and its people.

24:45.600 --> 24:47.240
Chu Ling and Chu Zhao

24:56.800 --> 24:58.120
have demonstrated steadfast loyalty,

24:58.200 --> 24:59.800
ever mindful of the greater good
of the state.

24:59.880 --> 25:01.800
The frontier is the shield of the state,

25:01.880 --> 25:03.240
upon which the state's security depends.

25:03.320 --> 25:05.960
Chu Ling, the Guard General,

25:06.480 --> 25:08.240
having stood guard at the frontier
for decades,

25:08.320 --> 25:11.040
repelled invaders and secured the state
with extraordinary feats.

25:11.120 --> 25:12.560
Chu Zhao, the Grand Princess,

25:12.640 --> 25:15.200
left the palace
to campaign in her father's stead.

25:15.280 --> 25:17.760
Peerless in valor,
united in purpose with her father,

25:17.840 --> 25:18.680
she expanded and defended the state.

25:18.760 --> 25:19.960
Their monumental achievements stand

25:20.040 --> 25:22.600
as a glorious example for all subjects
of the state to follow.

25:26.720 --> 25:29.320
Yet Xie Yanfang, head of the Xie Clan,

25:29.920 --> 25:31.120
steeped in generations of imperial favor

25:31.200 --> 25:32.400
and raised to one
of the Three Excellencies,

25:32.480 --> 25:34.680
was bound by duty
to serve with utter devotion

25:34.760 --> 25:35.680
and uphold the order of the realm.

25:36.280 --> 25:38.040
Instead, harboring treacherous intent

25:38.120 --> 25:39.520
<i>and behaving with monstrous depravity,</i>

25:39.600 --> 25:41.720
<i>he colluded</i>
<i>with the Northern Desert bandits</i>

25:41.800 --> 25:43.320
<i>to invite catastrophe,</i>

25:43.400 --> 25:47.520
<i>leaving the frontier ravaged by war</i>
<i>and the populace displaced.</i>

25:47.600 --> 25:49.400
<i>By forming internal factions</i>
<i>to purge the loyal,</i>

25:49.480 --> 25:51.160
<i>he sought to usurp power</i>

25:51.240 --> 25:55.080
<i>and deceive the throne,</i>
<i>his crimes too numerous to recount.</i>

25:55.680 --> 25:58.440
<i>Most abhorrent remains</i>
<i>the tragedy at Wei Village,</i>

25:58.520 --> 26:00.480
<i>where for personal gain,</i>

26:00.560 --> 26:03.200
<i>he emboldened foreign enemies</i>
<i>to commit arson and slaughter</i>

26:03.280 --> 26:05.640
-<i>to the entire village.</i>
-Help! Please help me!

26:06.240 --> 26:08.040
Such atrocities

26:08.120 --> 26:10.120
are beyond human reason,

26:10.200 --> 26:11.240
an abomination to all existence.

26:12.000 --> 26:13.520
The laws of this land are unyielding,

26:13.600 --> 26:15.440
and they will not stand
for such wicked defiance.

26:15.520 --> 26:17.240
Though I ascended the throne in my youth,

26:17.320 --> 26:20.200
I bear the legacy of my ancestors
and the trust of the people.

26:20.280 --> 26:23.560
<i>I shall act with uncompromising resolve</i>
<i>to purge all treachery and corruption.</i>

26:24.240 --> 26:27.040
<i>All titles and ranks</i>
<i>of the Xie Clan are hereby stripped.</i>

26:27.120 --> 26:30.080
<i>Their lands, estates, silver,</i>
<i>and valuables shall be confiscated.</i>

26:30.160 --> 26:31.480
<i>All adult males of the Xie Clan</i>

26:31.560 --> 26:32.920
<i>shall be beheaded forthwith.</i>

26:33.000 --> 26:34.360
<i>The women and children</i>

26:34.440 --> 26:35.680
<i>shall be exiled to the far frontier</i>
<i>as slaves.</i>

26:36.280 --> 26:38.400
<i>Any pupils, former subordinates,</i>
<i>or accomplices involved in his crimes</i>

26:38.480 --> 26:39.800
<i>must surrender within ten days.</i>

26:39.880 --> 26:42.120
<i>Those captured after the deadline</i>
<i>shall face punishment threefold.</i>

26:42.200 --> 26:45.000
This decree is proclaimed
across the state.

26:45.080 --> 26:46.240
Whoever colludes with the enemy,
betrays the state,

26:46.320 --> 26:49.200
or harms the people shall be executed

26:49.280 --> 26:50.560
with their entire clan,

26:50.640 --> 26:53.080
to uphold the laws of the state
and serve as a warning to all.

26:53.160 --> 26:55.120
May my ministers and I together

26:55.200 --> 26:57.560
purge this corruption
and restore a prosperous age.

26:58.480 --> 26:59.760
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

26:59.840 --> 27:02.840
Mr. Xie is your own in-law.

27:02.920 --> 27:03.800
Censor, mind your words.

27:04.400 --> 27:06.160
I am a Xiao, not a Xie.

27:07.120 --> 27:10.160
The state belongs to the Xiao Family.

27:10.240 --> 27:11.720
I bring down the Xie Family

27:11.800 --> 27:13.880
to save all the people.

27:14.640 --> 27:15.480
Issue the decree.

27:15.560 --> 27:17.000
Kowtow!

27:34.080 --> 27:37.040
Mr. Xie, His Majesty
has decreed that your clan be purged.

27:49.240 --> 27:50.120
What did you say?

27:50.960 --> 27:52.200
This is the imperial edict

27:52.280 --> 27:53.440
His Majesty announced
during this morning's court session.

27:54.120 --> 27:55.760
He proclaimed that Chu Ling
and Chu Zhao's monumental achievements

27:55.840 --> 27:56.960
shall be honored by the state,

27:57.040 --> 27:59.760
while you are guilty of heinous crimes,

27:59.840 --> 28:02.760
and your entire clan
is to be utterly eradicated.

28:12.160 --> 28:14.920
‎CHU FAMILY’S MERITS SHOULD INSPIRE ALL.
‎XIE YANGFANG‘S CRIMES ARE UNFORGIVABLE.

28:24.040 --> 28:25.320
Absurd.

28:27.760 --> 28:30.040
Profoundly absurd.

28:32.280 --> 28:33.600
How dare he?

28:37.960 --> 28:39.440
Mr. Xie, we must leave at once.

28:39.520 --> 28:41.320
The Imperial Guard
will reach Gaoyang shortly.

28:45.240 --> 28:46.280
Leave?

28:48.760 --> 28:49.840
Where to?

28:51.160 --> 28:53.040
Flee to the frontier

28:56.720 --> 28:58.560
or live in obscurity?

29:00.040 --> 29:02.280
How could I suffer

29:04.680 --> 29:07.600
such humiliation?

29:07.680 --> 29:09.960
Mr. Xie, while there is life,
there is hope.

29:10.040 --> 29:13.400
We leave now
and figure out the rest later.

29:28.040 --> 29:31.280
TAIJI HALL

29:43.160 --> 29:47.200
<i>Xie Yanfang betrayed the state…</i>

29:48.040 --> 29:52.400
<i>And opened the door</i>
<i>To the Northern Desert's blade</i>

29:55.960 --> 29:58.400
XIE RESIDENCE

30:02.840 --> 30:05.240
Zhao, it is over.

30:10.400 --> 30:11.640
Not yet.

30:40.240 --> 30:44.720
HONOR THE CLAN, UNITE THE KIN

30:51.040 --> 30:52.200
Your Highness,

30:53.600 --> 30:55.320
it took you long enough.

31:19.040 --> 31:20.120
Look.

31:21.280 --> 31:25.360
Yanlai has finally gotten
exactly what he wanted.

31:25.440 --> 31:26.720
TABLET OF XIE YANLAI

31:29.520 --> 31:31.480
I remember him arriving
at the Xie household

31:32.640 --> 31:34.520
at eight years old.

31:35.360 --> 31:39.760
He was so timid and fearful of everything.

31:39.840 --> 31:44.040
I held his hand and taught him to read…

31:44.120 --> 31:44.960
XIE YANLAI

31:45.040 --> 31:46.160
…and write.

31:46.760 --> 31:48.600
The very first character
he learned to write

31:50.480 --> 31:52.280
was Xie, as in our family name.

31:53.960 --> 31:55.320
I told him

31:56.800 --> 31:58.320
never to forget

31:59.360 --> 32:01.040
his last name.

32:03.560 --> 32:04.680
Yet

32:05.560 --> 32:07.800
the clan elders,
disdaining his lowly origins,

32:08.920 --> 32:11.240
refused to grant him the surname.

32:12.480 --> 32:14.520
So, I sent him to the Wei village
to handle that business,

32:15.560 --> 32:17.480
promising that if he succeeded,

32:18.120 --> 32:22.400
I would persuade the elders
to add him to the genealogy.

32:24.680 --> 32:26.400
Back then…

32:27.160 --> 32:28.480
he was over the moon.

32:30.200 --> 32:34.880
He never knew
that I was the one who took Xiang…

32:36.800 --> 32:40.960
making him the lone scapegoat
for the massacre at the Wei Village.

32:42.440 --> 32:45.320
And while he was investigating
the Xie Family's medicinal storage,

32:45.920 --> 32:50.160
I had Du Qi kill the boy.

32:52.760 --> 32:54.320
He was just a child.

32:55.440 --> 32:56.320
What did he ever do to deserve that?

32:56.400 --> 32:58.440
His only mistake

32:59.400 --> 33:01.120
was that, after five years of captivity,

33:01.800 --> 33:04.320
he still wanted to testify for Yanlai.

33:22.880 --> 33:24.280
The irony of it all…

33:26.320 --> 33:27.280
is that the life-saving pill

33:28.280 --> 33:31.120
is useless without the second pill.

33:31.200 --> 33:35.800
My intention was that
if Yanlai truly took it…

33:37.000 --> 33:38.800
I could save him

33:39.400 --> 33:41.440
when the poison set in,

33:42.040 --> 33:45.120
and he would be indebted to me for life.

33:48.320 --> 33:49.800
It comes back to me now.

33:51.560 --> 33:53.160
By a twist of fate,

33:53.920 --> 33:56.320
that is how your father met his end.

33:59.720 --> 34:01.840
Not entirely bad news, I suppose.

34:13.480 --> 34:14.639
Chu Zhao,

34:15.840 --> 34:17.960
you may bring down the Xie Family,

34:18.560 --> 34:20.840
but you cannot save Xie Yanlai.

34:22.040 --> 34:24.280
The Golden Finch Venom has no cure.

34:25.120 --> 34:26.639
He will die,

34:27.880 --> 34:31.440
and even before I do.

34:56.800 --> 35:00.240
Yanfang, despite all your calculating,

35:00.840 --> 35:03.400
you are still one move behind.

35:23.560 --> 35:24.960
Yanlai?

35:26.040 --> 35:27.480
Impossible.

35:30.280 --> 35:32.480
How are you still alive?

35:33.440 --> 35:34.720
Because all of this

35:36.480 --> 35:39.040
was a trap laid carefully for you.

35:40.000 --> 35:42.400
This dagger is forged with two sides,

35:43.400 --> 35:45.120
distinguished by gold and silver.

35:46.160 --> 35:49.360
I will coat the gold side
with Golden Finch Venom in advance.

35:50.880 --> 35:53.680
We are going to stage a death scene
right before his eyes.

35:54.960 --> 35:56.720
You will strike yourself
with the silver, non-poisonous blade.

35:56.800 --> 35:57.840
The wound, however,

35:58.960 --> 35:59.920
must look absolutely real.

36:01.520 --> 36:02.960
<i>Only a lie built upon a grain of truth</i>

36:03.040 --> 36:04.760
<i>can deceive them all.</i>

36:04.840 --> 36:07.040
<i>I will play the part of a hostage,</i>
<i>forced back to the court</i>

36:08.080 --> 36:09.800
to serve as his puppet, day after day.

36:17.320 --> 36:18.800
I could kill Xie Yanfang,

36:19.680 --> 36:21.400
-even at the cost of my own life.
-No.

36:21.480 --> 36:25.200
There will always be another Xie Yanfang.

36:25.720 --> 36:26.960
We must leverage
the Xie Family's influence

36:27.040 --> 36:28.280
to keep the court in check,

36:28.800 --> 36:29.840
until Yu takes the reins.

36:30.960 --> 36:31.880
Yes, Your Highness.

36:34.880 --> 36:38.000
<i>From that moment on,</i>
<i>everything you saw was a lie.</i>

36:39.640 --> 36:41.680
<i>I knew you were</i>
<i>after the Frontier Troops Token,</i>

36:41.760 --> 36:45.040
<i>so I instructed Zhong to feign submission.</i>

36:46.000 --> 36:47.240
<i>What I failed to account for</i>

36:48.240 --> 36:49.360
<i>was how far you would sink,</i>

36:49.440 --> 36:50.760
<i>raising your blades</i>
<i>against the Longwei Army.</i>

36:51.280 --> 36:52.960
This is the medicine Xie Yanfang sent.

36:53.480 --> 36:55.280
<i>Using the cover of my convalescence</i>
<i>at Cangmu Stronghold,</i>

36:55.360 --> 36:57.720
<i>I've been quietly gathering evidence</i>
<i>of the Xie Family's crimes.</i>

36:58.240 --> 37:00.920
<i>Yet you were so intoxicated</i>
<i>by the thrill of pulling every string</i>

37:01.000 --> 37:01.880
<i>that you let your guard down entirely.</i>

37:01.960 --> 37:03.880
<i>The officials you have promoted</i>

37:03.960 --> 37:06.560
<i>also allowed me to compile a complete list</i>
<i>of the Xie Family's faction</i>

37:06.640 --> 37:08.040
<i>within the court.</i>

37:08.120 --> 37:09.280
<i>Jiu and I</i>

37:09.880 --> 37:12.200
<i>have always been working behind your back,</i>

37:12.280 --> 37:14.760
<i>tirelessly molding Yu</i>
<i>into a capable ruler.</i>

37:15.280 --> 37:18.160
Yunzhong Prefecture is
the frontier stronghold of the Capital,

37:18.240 --> 37:19.080
easy to defend and hard to breach.

37:19.680 --> 37:22.240
But should the Northern Desert resolve
its internal strife, return with force,

37:22.320 --> 37:23.920
and bring the surrounding minor states
into the fold,

37:24.000 --> 37:26.200
a flanking assault could spell trouble.

37:26.280 --> 37:28.120
May I then send envoys

37:28.200 --> 37:29.680
to build ties with neighboring states
and avoid war?

37:29.760 --> 37:31.720
A wise thought, Your Majesty.

37:32.680 --> 37:33.600
Military strength and diplomacy

37:34.200 --> 37:36.800
are both essential
to the art of governance.

37:36.880 --> 37:39.440
Bear in mind that the greatest victory
is to avoid war.

37:39.520 --> 37:42.000
<i>Peace is what endures.</i>

37:43.640 --> 37:44.480
<i>Hold the sword as you would a fist.</i>

37:45.360 --> 37:47.880
<i>Loosen your grip even once,</i>
<i>and all is lost.</i>

37:49.160 --> 37:50.920
<i>Zhao, I understand.</i>

37:52.600 --> 37:54.360
Ruling is like a game of strategy.

37:54.440 --> 37:56.120
It matters not who moves first,

37:56.200 --> 37:58.840
only who has the last laugh.

38:02.480 --> 38:04.040
Much like what you are doing now.

38:12.760 --> 38:16.400
Yanfang, you always said
the noble families were deeply entangled.

38:17.640 --> 38:19.040
So we learned from you,

38:19.840 --> 38:23.040
traced each root to its source,

38:23.120 --> 38:25.920
and pulled them all out.

38:33.520 --> 38:34.520
Yanlai,

38:35.560 --> 38:38.840
since you are alive, why not come home?

38:40.440 --> 38:41.720
After I pass away,

38:41.800 --> 38:44.840
the immense power of the Xie Family
and the position of clan head

38:44.920 --> 38:46.520
will all be yours.

38:47.920 --> 38:50.080
Why make such a choice?

38:51.760 --> 38:53.680
What exactly are you trying to do?

38:55.400 --> 38:57.560
No one reads hearts well as you do.

38:59.240 --> 39:02.600
How can you not know that what I want

39:03.880 --> 39:07.080
is to take the Xie Family's
century-old legacy with me to the grave?

39:21.240 --> 39:23.560
The clan elders must regret not killing me

39:24.920 --> 39:26.560
when they could,

39:27.560 --> 39:30.240
only for me, too low-born
to enter the genealogy

39:32.880 --> 39:34.280
to end the Xie's bloodline for good.

39:35.280 --> 39:36.320
Yanlai.

39:37.960 --> 39:40.440
Seeing you like this, so deranged,

39:41.880 --> 39:43.960
I almost see myself.

39:47.880 --> 39:48.880
Indeed.

39:49.920 --> 39:52.200
I am the baby wolf
you spent years shaping.

39:54.880 --> 39:57.840
Remember, my brother?

40:00.920 --> 40:02.280
We've won

40:03.800 --> 40:05.560
this game after all.

40:06.520 --> 40:07.560
Good.

40:09.520 --> 40:10.920
Splendid.

40:16.560 --> 40:18.760
TABLET OF XIE YANLAI

40:19.760 --> 40:23.920
Yanfang, do you know
why you lost this game?

40:26.400 --> 40:29.400
For all your plotting,
you forgot one thing.

40:30.840 --> 40:34.880
The most brilliant schemes
are the ones that ensnare their maker.

40:36.440 --> 40:38.160
Xie Yanfang, you were so confident

40:38.240 --> 40:40.720
that you never doubted you were the one
moving the pieces.

40:40.800 --> 40:46.120
Little did you know the very web you wove
would be the one to close around you.

40:47.600 --> 40:48.440
Surprising, isn't it?

40:50.200 --> 40:51.280
The piece

40:52.040 --> 40:54.120
you thought to command at will

40:55.200 --> 40:58.720
has made you a discarded pawn of fate.

41:15.400 --> 41:18.640
Mr. Xie, Her Highness is but a woman.

41:18.720 --> 41:19.560
What does she have

41:19.640 --> 41:21.760
that makes you treat her so differently?

41:23.280 --> 41:24.280
She is…

41:26.320 --> 41:27.200
different.

41:28.680 --> 41:29.520
Chu Zhao.

41:48.280 --> 41:49.840
A move made is a move set.

41:51.080 --> 41:52.320
I lost.

41:53.440 --> 41:54.520
And I own it.

42:06.200 --> 42:12.840
HONOR THE CLAN, UNITE THE KIN

42:27.840 --> 42:31.640
<i>I see no difference between people.</i>

42:32.360 --> 42:36.480
<i>But once a difference appears,</i>
<i>the heart tilts.</i>

42:37.000 --> 42:42.600
<i>And a tilted heart becomes a prison.</i>

42:47.680 --> 42:48.840
From this day onward…

42:48.920 --> 42:49.680
DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

42:49.760 --> 42:52.920
…taxes across all prefectures
shall be reduced by 30%.

42:53.000 --> 42:55.080
-Your Majesty is wise.
-Your Majesty is wise.

42:55.160 --> 42:57.880
Furthermore, the laws of the State of Chu
shall be revised.

42:58.720 --> 43:01.160
<i>Anyone found colluding with foreign powers</i>

43:01.240 --> 43:02.600
<i>shall be held collectively responsible,</i>

43:02.680 --> 43:03.520
<i>and their entire clan</i>
<i>shall be exterminated.</i>

43:03.600 --> 43:05.600
IN 5TH YEAR OF XINGPING, XIE FACTION FELL.
EMPEROR RESUMES POWER. A NEW ERA BEGINS

43:10.760 --> 43:12.960
SERVE WITH LOYALTY, GUARD WITH DILIGENCE

43:19.840 --> 43:22.040
IMPERIAL GUARD OFFICE

44:33.600 --> 44:35.560
No luck with the hares,
so you're after me now?

44:35.640 --> 44:37.600
You're just easier to catch.

44:38.120 --> 44:40.280
Every creature on these grasslands
is cunning.

44:43.840 --> 44:44.920
I just had

44:46.200 --> 44:47.360
a nightmare.

44:49.000 --> 44:50.880
So even you have fears, General Xie?

44:52.400 --> 44:54.320
In the dream, death tore us apart.

44:57.320 --> 44:58.840
Don't say that.

44:59.680 --> 45:01.200
We still have many years ahead of us.

45:02.800 --> 45:03.760
Agreed.

45:05.840 --> 45:08.080
Then we shall guard
Yunzhong Prefecture side by side,

45:08.800 --> 45:10.080
day after day,

45:11.000 --> 45:12.200
year after year,

45:12.720 --> 45:13.880
to the very end.

45:16.560 --> 45:21.760
I intend to expand
the place where I used to live.

45:22.880 --> 45:24.360
Why the rush to renovate?

45:25.200 --> 45:26.240
There is every reason.

45:38.120 --> 45:39.600
I want to marry you.

45:42.080 --> 45:43.000
Let's build a home together.

45:44.680 --> 45:45.760
What do you say?

46:22.240 --> 46:25.360
<i>In the 11th month</i>
<i>of the 13th year of Xingping,</i>

46:25.440 --> 46:27.680
<i>the Grand Princess withdrew</i>
<i>into seclusion on account of illness.</i>

46:28.200 --> 46:31.720
<i>The Yunzhong frontier troops</i>
<i>established the Princess's encampment.</i>
